Class Employee

  • java.lang.Object
    • homework.Employee

  • public abstract class Employee
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is extended by the hourlyEmployee , ComissionEmployee, BasePlusComissionEmployee and SalariedEmployee. It basically connects all the workers and computes their earnings each pay period.
